<template>
<svg width="90" height="60" viewBox="0 0 90 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="empty-map-svg">
<rect x="15" y="20" width="60" height="25" rx="8" fill="#A0C4FF" opacity="0.25" />
<path class="map-shape" d="M25,40 Q35,25 45,35 Q55,45 65,25 Q75,40 55,45 Q35,55 25,40 Z" fill="#4F8EF7" />
<circle class="map-dot" cx="45" cy="35" r="4" fill="#FFB300" />
</svg>
</template>

<script setup>
</script>

<style scoped>
.empty-map-svg {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: floatX 3.2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.map-shape {
    opacity: 0.85;
    animation: map-pop 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,1.6,.6,1) infinite alternate;
}
.map-dot {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: dot-pop 0.7s cubic-bezier(.4,1.6,.6,1) forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.8s;
}
@keyframes map-pop {
    0% { transform: scale(0.8); }
    60% { transform: scale(1.1); }
    100% { transform: scale(0.8); }
}
@keyframes dot-pop {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
    60% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.2); }
    100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
}
@keyframes floatX {
    0% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
    25% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px) translateX(-4px); }
    75% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
}
</style>
